description: Seamless Distribution Systems AB engages in the provision of electronic systems and mobile payment services for telecommunications, distribution, and retail industries. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm. The company went IPO on 2017-07-21. The company is a software development company that specializes in technology solutions for mobile operators, banks, grocery stores and distributors. Seamless Distribution Systems AB's main business and product area is the digital distribution of airtime and mobile data for mobile telephony providers by offering systems for the electronic top-up of prepaid cards and support and Managed Operations (MOPS) associated with such systems. Seamless Distribution Systems AB is present in more than 27 markets and has teams based in Sweden, Belgium, Ghana, Guinea Conakry, the United States, Pakistan, India and the United Arab Emirates.
name: Seamless Distribution Systems AB
